# ECHO         FreeBSD 10.3 Refined unix kernel & World

Unix clones built to form a homogeneous OTOPSKOPIE network.

OTO  - One Time Only
PSK  - Pre Shared Keys
OPIE - One Password In Everything

This kernel is aimed for an explicit-only compilation of modules. 

1) The kernel is first filtered via the kernel build via /etc/src.conf.
2) KERN is the kernel configuration file that further sculpts & hardens the kernel
3) /etc/sysctl.conf is the optional element
4) Jail buildworld is stripped via a special src.conf & SCRAPE.pl

LAYERS:
HOST_KERNEL OPIE | NFS JAIL | USERLAND OPIE JAIL | ANONYMOUS OTOPSK JAIL

Escalation is refined su groups
